== About ==

This extension enables installation and updating of extensions and MediaWiki itself.
It obtains deployment packages by using the API provided by the Distribution extension [0],
parses these and applies them. For this it provides several special pages. More info at [1].

[0] https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/mediawiki/wiki/Extension:Distribution
[1] https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/mediawiki/wiki/Extension:Deployment

